      </p>
      <p>
        Before installing an electric underfloor heating mat or cable, always consult the manufacturer's installation instructions for your specific heating system. This ensures compatibility with your chosen floor covering and helps avoid common pitfalls, setting the stage for a successful and long-lasting underfloor heating solution.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

