  </section>

  <!-- SOLAR PANELS INTEGRATION -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium mb-6">Solar Panels and Electric Underfloor Heating</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Pairing solar panels with electric underfloor heating systems is an excellent way to create an energy efficient and environmentally friendly heating solution. By generating your own renewable electricity, you can power your underfloor heating system, significantly reducing your energy consumption and reliance on the grid. This combination not only lowers running costs but also supports a more sustainable lifestyle.
